metadata.name: The Eye
metadata.description:
Photo: 5504  x  8256

The First time I've visited this place was half a year ago, during scouting for new locations. I've immediately become curious about this arch. Opened the planner app (photo pills) and - saw "The Eye'' (and it looked at me). Now all I needed was to wait 6 months, to perfectly position Milky Way 
 
Shooting itself was very exciting, I knew what to expect. The only hope was not to be spoiled by clouds. For my fortune, the sky started to be cloudy, exactly after I did the required shoot 
Image is taken at Timna Valley.
